if exists (select 1
from sysobjects

and type = 'U')
drop table busi_orderproduct

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: busi_orderproduct */
/*==============================================================*/
create table busi_orderproduct (
OrderProID int not null,
OrderID int not null,
PackID int not null,
ProID int not null,
SkuID int not null,
SKUCode nvarchar(100) null,
Num int not null,
ProductName nvarchar(1000) null,
PicUrl nvarchar(200) null,
AppTime datetime not null default getdate(),
IsDel bit not null default 0,
Weight int null,
Remark nvarchar(200) null,
status int null,
depotID int null,
prosource int null,
price decimal(10,2) null,
constraint PK_BUSI_ORDERPRODUCT primary key (OrderProID)
)
go
